.TH UBANNER 1 2024-03-23 "ubanner 0"
.SH NAME
ubanner \- Unicode-enabled banner(1)-like program
.SH SYNOPSIS
.SY ubanner
.RB [ \-\-trim ]
.RB [ \-f " \fIFONT\fP]"
.RB [ \-s " \fIN\fP]"
.RB [ \-S ]
.RI [ TEXT " ...]"
.YS
.SY ubanner
.B \-\-list\-fonts
.YS
.IP
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-trim
Trim leading and trailing empty lines.
.TP
.BR \-f ", " \-\-font " \fIFONT\fP"
Set font face to
.IR FONT .
.TP
.BR \-s ", " \-\-font\-size " \fIN\fP"
Set font size to
.IR N " pixels."
The default is 28.
.TP
.BR \-S ", " \-\-full\-screen
Use the maximum font size to fit the terminal window.
.TP
.BR \-\-list\-fonts
Print the list of available font faces.
.TP
.BR -h ", " \-\-help
Show help message and exit.
.TP
.B \-\-version
Show version information and exit.
